* Clarence Lusane and Dennis Desmond, &quot;Pipe Dream Blues: Racism and the War on Drugs&quot;, South End Press, 1991, .
* United Nations Office on Drugs and Crime, &quot;Colombian Survey&quot;, June 2005.
