<text>Sewer commonly refers to a part of sewerage, the infrastructure that conveys sewage.

Types of sewers include:

* Combined sewer
*Effluent sewer
*Gravity sewer
*Sanitary sewer
*Storm sewer
*Vacuum sewer
Other uses:
*Sewer, one who does sewing

